Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I like walking around Shibuya at night.}Mình thích đi bộ quanh Shibuya ban đêm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:17.13,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Jellyfish are not capable of swimming on their own.}Sứa không thể tự bơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:25.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{When I'm in a town where no one recognizes me,\Ndrifting around as aimlessly as a jellyfish,}Khi ở một nơi xa lạ, mình lang thang\N khắp nơi không sợ ai nhận ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:31.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I don't have to worry about who might be watching.}Không phải lo lắng có ai đang nhìn mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:37.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{They simply drift, going along with the flow of the water.}Chúng chỉ đơn giản là trôi nổi trong nước.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{When I walk surrounded by colorful neon lights,}Khi bước dưới ánh đèn neon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:43.92,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I feel as if I'm shining, too.}mình cảm thấy bản thân đang toả sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:45.13,Q1,,0,0,0,,{560,000 yen?! Yikes!}560.000 yên?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:48.96,Q0,,0,0,0,,{They may seem like fragile creatures,}Chúng tuy trông mong manh dễ vỡ,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:52.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{but they actually have quite an incredible trait.}nhưng có một đặc điểm kinh ngạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:54.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{And that trait is...}Và đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:55.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Whoa!}Oa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:04.92,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hey Sis? You're gonna be late to school!}Chị! Trễ học đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:12.67,Q0,,0,0,0,,{My name is Mahiru Kouzuki, age 17,\Nliving in Omiya Ward of Saitama City-}Tên tôi là Kouzuki Mahiru, 17 tuổi, \Nsống ở Omiya, thành phố Saitama--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:15.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Kaho, that's not okay. Delete it.}Kaho, xoá đi ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:16.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Aw, what?}Gì chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:20.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But sleeping faces of actual high school girls\Nis the most coveted content in the world!}Nhưng khuôn mặt ngái ngủ của nữ sinh\N cấp 3 là nội dung nhiều người thích nhất đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:22.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{This'll go viral for sure!}Chắc chắn sẽ bùng nổ luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:25.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Elementary school kids shouldn't\Nbe talking about going viral!}Mới học tiểu học thì đừng có đua đòi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:30.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Besides, ordinary high school girls\Non PikPok are a dime a dozen.}Với cả nữ sinh cấp 3 chơi Pik Pok cũng đầy mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:33.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I don't even have makeup on. No one wants that.}Chị còn chưa trang điểm nữa. Chẳng ai thèm xem đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:33.83,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:35.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's power abuse!}Đó là bắt nạt đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:36.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{How, may I ask?}Chỗ nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:38.96,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Why don't you get going to school?}Cơ mà em không đi học à?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:40.83,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You don't get it, do you?}Chị chẳng hiểu gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:45.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{These days, going viral makes much\Nmore money than going to school.}Thời nay làm hot Pikpoker \Nkiếm nhiều tiền hơn đi học đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's right, I'm gonna be an influencer!}Em sẽ trở thành infuencer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:47.96,Q1,,0,0,0,,{Kaho.}Kaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:52.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Better not post photos of you goofing off in the display\Nfridge at your part-time job when you grow up.}Tương lai đừng có đăng cảnh em\N chui vô tủ đông ở chỗ làm thêm đó nha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:53.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:56.17,Q2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(473.6,86.4)}{\an7}{got in the fridge lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:56.17,Q2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(691.2,475.2)}{\an7}{on the job lmao}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:56.17,Q3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(460.8,532.8)}{\an7}{Rampant Pranking on the Job}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{"Pranking on the job"?}Đùa giỡn lúc làm việc?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:58.88,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You can't cause trouble for other people, you hear?}Đừng có làm ảnh hưởng đến người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:00.88,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I'm not that immature.}Em không có trẻ trâu thế đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:04.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Ooh. But look at you.}Cơ mà chị nhìn lại mình đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You're actually pretty childish yourself.}Y như mấy đứa nhóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:11.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,Có sao đâu! Ai thèm quan tâm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:13.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Meanwhile, you always go for clothing\Nand makeup that don't stand out.}Quần áo với trang điểm chẳng nổi bật gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:19.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Um, hello? This lipstick was featured by Yukochi,\Nwho has like 300k followers, okay?}Này nhé, thỏi son được Yukochi, \N300k người theo dõi khuyên dùng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:20.96,Q0,,0,0,0,,{It's as cute as it gets!}Dĩ nhiên là dễ thương rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:27.83,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Nuh-uh. That only looks good on her 'cuz she's\Nfair-skinned with a tiny face and a nose like Cleopatra's!}Không nhé, vì chị ấy có làn da trắng như Cleopatra\N và mặt nhỏ nhắn nên mới hợp thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:28.96,Q0,,0,0,0,,Cleopatra...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:32.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But when some ordinary girl copies that look...}Nhưng khi một nữ sinh bắt chước theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.67,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Uh, what if she does?}Thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:36.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What, what, what, what, what?}Này này này, gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{She's just becomes run-of-the-mill.}Chỉ là một đứa tầm thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What?! But it's Halloween!}Hả? Hallween đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:50.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I mean, we can go, but do we have to get\Nserious about the whole costume thing?}Ừ thì đi nhưng chúng ta phải ăn diện đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I know, right?}Nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:57.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Well sure, but I wanna prove I'm worth\Nsomething before I die, you know?!}Ừ thì... nhưng tớ cũng muốn chứng tỏ\N giá trị bản thân trước khi chết!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:02:59.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I can kinda understand that.}A, tớ cũng hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:00.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Right?!}Phải chứ?
