Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:24.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hey, don't call me that!}Này, đừng có gọi tớ thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:26.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I gave up the whole drawing thing years ago.}Tớ bỏ vễ lâu lắm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh, that's right.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:32.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Us high school girls have to focus on\Nwhat's in front of us. And that's all we really want.}Nữ sinh trung học nên tập trung vào\N những gì trước mắt, thế là đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Right, Mahiru?}Nhỉ, Mahiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Totally.}Ừm, đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But you don't actually think so.}Nhưng cậu không nghĩ vậy nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Well, that's why I needed to vent.}Thế nên tớ mới cần chỗ để xả nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:46.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's pretty messy. You managing okay?}Khá là phiền phức đó. Ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:49.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{As blunt as ever, I see.}Vẫn thẳng thắn như mọi khi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:50.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Well, yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.13,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's why Nox Ryugasaki's so popular.}Đó là lý do Ryugasaki Nox nổi tiếng mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.54,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Of course. You know what you're talking about, Kiui.}Phải nhỉ. Không hổ danh là Kiui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:00.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{No wonder you're Tatekita's student council president!}Đúng là hội trưởng hội học sinh Tatekita.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:06.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But honestly, I was kind of\Nthinking the same thing as her.}Cơ mà tớ cũng nghĩ giống cậu ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.17,Q8,,0,0,0,,{Are these for real?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.04,Q9,,0,0,0,,{Who would wear these?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:08.96,Q9,,0,0,0,,{Mero, see all your fans gathered outside?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:10.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{It's not that I just want to wear a flashy costume.}Cũng không hẳn là tớ muốn ăn diện.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:09.88,Q9,,0,0,0,,{I do!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:16.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But I do get the feeling of wanting\Nto be someone other than yourself.}Nhưng cảm giác trở thành người khác ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Then you should've just said so.}Vậy thì cứ thẳng thắn nói ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I can't, that's the problem!}Vấn đề là không thể nói đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Getting shot down when\Nyou're being honest is so cringey.}Bị bàn tán khi sống thật phiền phức lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:29.96,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You've always been a scaredy-cat, Mahiru.}Cậu lúc nào cũng nhát gan nhỉ, Mahiru.
