Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah!}Quá đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:53.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{The strong stuff sure hits the spot!}Uống strongbow để strong hơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:57.79,Q11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(588.8,511.2)}{\an7}{I wanna quit!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.88,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's so specific it cracks me up.}Hiện thực quá đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:57.71,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Don't wanna end up like that, y'know?}Tớ không muốn như thế đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Then what exactly do you want to be?}Vậy chứ muốn như nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:02.58,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Well...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Nothing in particular.}Không muốn gì cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:07.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Nothing?!}Không gì cả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:12.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{If anything, I want to be someone who knows what\Nshe wants to be, or knows what she likes, I guess?}Nếu có thì chắc muốn thành\N người biết rõ bản thân muốn gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's a conundrum.}Nghe khó hiểu thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:21.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I've got my streaming, song recording, and video editing.\NThere's tons of stuff I wanna do.}Còn tớ thì phải strem, ghi âm bài hát, \Nchỉnh sửa video, nhiều việc muốn làm lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.96,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Mahiru? Are you listening?}Mahiru? Có nghe không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.13,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh! Sorry, what were we talking about?}A, nói về chuyện gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.13,Q12,,0,0,0,,{\pos(281.6,295.2)}{\an7}{Sold Out}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{About what you want to be.}Về việc cậu muốn trở thành gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You're special, Kiui.}Cậu là đặc biệt, Kiui.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:40.58,Q0,,0,0,0,,{When you're just an ordinary high school girl like me,\Nyou gotta wait to be chosen. You don't get to choose.}Còn tớ chỉ là một nữ sinh trung học bình thường, \Nphải chờ đợi để được chọn.
