Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Uh, what's with the weird drawing?}Bức tranh kì lạ gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:26.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:29.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Jellyfish graffiti? The colors are so weird.}Tranh tường sứa? Màu sắc gì kì vậy?
