Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:32.92,Q0,,0,0,0,,{No, we'd get in trouble!}Đừng, bị mắng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.58,Q0,,0,0,0,,{It'll be fine! It's weird enough already.}Không sao! Ban đầu nó cũng kì lạ rồi.
