Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,Ừm, phải đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:44.67,Q0,,0,0,0,,{It's super weird, isn't it?}Đúng là kì lạ nhỉ.
