Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:49.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{It's not like I have any right to say that.}Mình cũng không có quyền nói vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:50.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:51.75,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:56.83,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Don't go defiling that mural I love!}Đừng có làm ô uế bức tranh tường tôi thích!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:02.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What, you mean this old scribble?}Gì thế? Bức vẽ nguệch ngoạc này á?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:05.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{It's not a scribble! It's a picture of jellyfish!}Đừng có nói thế! Là bức vẽ con sứa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{This?}Cái này á?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:07.83,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Wait, aren't you...}Khoan, cậu là...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:24.50,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Oh, come on! Are you kidding?!\NWhy wouldja lose, Hamanoumi?!}Đùa à? Sao lại thua thế hả, Hamanoumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's no good.}Không ổn chút nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.00,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Okay, what am I, a stalker?}Sao mình lại bám đuôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Still!}Nhưng!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Well, that's how these things go.}Cũng phải thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I mean, what would I have-}Cơ mà gặp rồi nói--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Hey. You keep following me.}Cậu bám theo tôi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:54.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Are you a stalker? Or bent on doxing me?}Bám đuôi? Hay tính tung tin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.54,Q0,,0,0,0,,{"D-doxing"?}T-Tung tin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:59.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Uh, no! I mean, I can't deny\NI was stalking you, pretty much.}Không không! Đúng là có bám theo cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You said it yourself. Let's call the cops.}Tự khai nhé. Lên đồn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.29,Q0,,0,0,0,,{No, no, that's not it!}Không, không phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:06.92,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Um, earlier... you raised your voice at the live street gig.}Lúc nãy...cậu đã la lên ở buổi diễn nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:08.96,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Sure I did. So?}Ừ thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:11.13,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You said you liked that mural.}Cậu nói thích bức tranh đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, so what?}Thì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Uh, you see...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I'm the one who painted that!}Tớ là người đã vẽ nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:22.33,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I-I have proof.}C-Có bằng chứng!
