Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.75,Q22,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.4,201.6)}{\an7}{I've been drawing jellyfish nonstop...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Though I cringe when I think about it.}Tuy là tài khoản hồi còn trẻ trâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:32.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But, yeah I know...\NThat's no excuse for me following you...}Ừm thì... tớ biết đó không phải lý do bám đuôi cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.79,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I'm a HUGE fan!}Tớ là fan lớn của cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:36.96,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
