Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Y-you've liked my art from before?}C-Cậu thích từ hồi xưa hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:47.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! Back in middle school, my dad\Nbrought me to Shibuya for the first time.}Phải! Hồi cấp 2, ba tớ dẫn lên Shibuya lần đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.38,Q0,,0,0,0,,{I saw that mural and it was love at first sight!}Khi thấy bức vẽ đó tớ đã bị mê hoặc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{L-love at first sight...}M-Mê hoặc...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:56.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{So? Why were you following me?}Thế sao cậu bám theo tớ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.92,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Uh, well...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Yeah?}Sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:04.83,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You defended my mural so... ou.}Lúc nãy cậu đã bảo vệ bức vẽ đó... nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:05.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.88,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You defended my mural, so thank you!}Cảm ơn cậu vì đã bảo vệ nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.92,Q0,,0,0,0,,{That's probably what I wanted to say.}Tớ chỉ muốn nói thế thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:13.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Uh, I think?}Chắc vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:17.21,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Actually, never mind.}Cơ mà bỏ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:20.17,Q0,,0,0,0,,{This is coming out so painfully awkward.}Sao tự nhiên khó xử vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.54,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Glad to hear it, thanks!}Vui quá. Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:25.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You're awfully sincere, Yoru.}Cậu chân thành ghê, Yoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Yoru?}Hả? Yoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:30.13,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Isn't that what you go by?\NOr do you prefer your actual name?}Thì cậu tự gọi mình là thế mà? \NHay thích gọi tên thật hơn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:33.63,Q0,,0,0,0,,{No. Sounds good. Call me Yoru.}Không sao. Gọi tớ Yoru cũng được.
