Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.04,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Who said I quit?}Ai nói tớ từ bỏ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:08.25,Q0,,0,0,0,,{But you said "former pop idol."}Thì cậu nói từng là idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:09.42,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You haven't?}Không phải à?
