Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.96,Q0,,0,0,0,,{This is who I am now!}Đó là tớ bây giờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.92,Q0,,0,0,0,,{What is this? An octopus? Or a squid?}Gì đây? Mực? Bạch tuộc?
