Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:34.54,Q0,,0,0,0,,{A jellyfish?!}Sứa á?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.46,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Then by JELEE...}Vậy Jelee là...
