Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.54,Q0,,0,0,0,,{Huh, okay.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:54.08,Q0,,0,0,0,,{You're more ordinary than I thought, Yoru.}Cậu bình thường hơn tớ nghĩ nhỉ, Yoru.
